			<td>Selenium</td>
			<td>0.05</td>
			<td>0.05</td>
			<td>
			<p>Hair or fingernail loss; numbness in fingers or toes; circulatory problems</p>
			</td>
			<td>
			<p>Discharge from petroleum refineries; erosion of natural deposits; discharge from mines</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td height="70">Thallium</td>
			<td>0.0005</td>
			<td>0.002</td>
			<td>
			<p>Hair loss; changes in blood; kidney, intestine, or liver problems</p>
			</td>
			<td>
			<p>Leaching from ore-processing sites; discharge from electronics, glass, and drug factories</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>


