<h3><a id="PFAS" name="PFAS"><strong>Selected Per- and poly-fluoroalkyl substances (PFAS)</strong></a></h3>

<table class="tablebord zebra" summary="Information on the Maximum Contaminant Level Goal, the Maximum Contaminant Level or Treatment Technique, and the health effects and sources for contaminants under the Radionuclides catagory.">
